Limpy<br>
(Kyril 53rd Mage) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ussslippy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SSSlippy</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Conjurer</span><br>  Posts: 277<br> <font color=#333333>(8/6/02 1:10:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels4950.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Echo Caverns</span><hr size=1> Echo Caverns, Ive been on and off there.  Depending u can clear the room before skeletons and keep up a constant killing.  By the time I can kill everything there the room starts respawning.  Its good exp and I believe it has a exp bonus.  Its inside so it should in theory.  I get 1% exp a kill at level 47 now.  You can also take the 4 entrance spawns down below.  They are lower level but they have a pain repop time.  I also discovered people can be very rude when u are there and just take the mobs.  Some guy did that and I yelled at him in gnomish and he looked at my funny. LoL <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=wyndor>Wyndor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#333333>(8/7/02 4:37:07 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels4950.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=13>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Hey Slippy</span><hr size=1> Could a 46 mage take em with not much mana gear and 152 int? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=zimzalabim>Zimzalabim</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#333333>(9/22/02 1:17:11 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels4950.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=130.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_smile.gif" align=absmiddle>  trolls in rathe..again</span><hr size=1> These are really good at 45. Perhaps there are better places at 45 but I dont know. Im lvl46 now and my play time is 14days, 12hours. So its pure xp for me that counts. <br>
<br>
At 45 these give 1/4 blue per kill. And with 2 spawns (6min) thats 1 blue in 12min. 5blue in 1h. And the lvl in 5,5h.<br>
<br>
The loot was around 4-500plat, including selling FS (common)<br>
<br>
And its 100%safe too. earth pet. Dont bother with DS or weapons. Just give him a summoned plate. Sen pet. Maelstrom. wait 10sec. Blaze or SoS finish. Easy! <br>
<br>
No aggro or bad pulls.<br>
